  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table width=&quot;100%&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; cellspacing=&quot;3&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; class=&quot;table table-bordered table-hover&quot; data-object-name=&quot;AssessmentConditionsPhraseMap&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 1749px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); table-layout: fixed;&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr id=&quot;row_141693&quot; class=&quot;entry&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);&quot;&gt;&lt;td name=&quot;Detail&quot; data-field-name=&quot;standard_phrase_paragraph&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-339d49ff-7fff-60c4-7023-916b30096a6e&quot;&gt;The material of the outrigger extension has not been confirmed to be similar to that used on the existing roof.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;As a result, the proposed development would not be permitted development and would not accord with Schedule 2, Part 1, Class B.2, (a) of the General Permitted Development Order 2015 (as amended).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);&quot;&gt;The proposed outrigger roof extension would not join the original roof of the existing dwellinghouse, as described by the Permitted Development Rights&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-d6d90b33-7fff-40d4-c33e-732663c41b83&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt; for Householders Technical Guidance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;As a result, the proposed development would not be permitted development and would not accord with Schedule 2, Part 1, Class B.2, (b) (ii) of the General Permitted Development Order 2015&amp;nbsp;(as amended).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
